IMPORTANT NOTE ON THE FIRMWARE BINARY

This repository also contains a firmware binary file (firmware/2268_v309.bin)
that was obtained through the official Attack Shark web updater. This binary
is proprietary software belonging to the original manufacturer (Attack
Shark) and is NOT covered by the MIT License above. It is included here
solely for archival and recovery purposes, to help users whose keyboards
become stuck in bootloader mode when the vendor's own backend is unable to
serve the firmware. No rights to the firmware itself are claimed or granted
by this repository or its author. If the manufacturer objects to the
distribution of this file, please open an Issue and it will be removed
promptly.
